Dasaka
Kusalattika
Saṃsaṭṭhavāra
Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Nahetuduka
Dasaka
797Nahetupaccayā naadhipatipaccayā napurejātapaccayā napacchājātapaccayā naāsevanapaccayā nakammapaccayā navipākapaccayā namaggapaccayā navippayuttapaccayā ārammaṇe ekaṃ, anantare ekaṃ, samanantare ekaṃ, sahajāte ekaṃ, aññamaññe ekaṃ, nissaye ekaṃ, upanissaye ekaṃ, āhāre ekaṃ, indriye ekaṃ, jhāne ekaṃ, sampayutte ekaṃ, atthiyā ekaṃ, natthiyā ekaṃ, vigate ekaṃ, avigate ekaṃ. (Navipākaṃ namaggaṃ navippayuttaṃ nakammapaccayasadisaṃ.)
